            <title>[CASSANDRA-8122] Undeclare throwable exception while executing &apos;nodetool netstats localhost&apos;</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-8122</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Steps&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
